I get about 4-5 hours a night, most nights.  Every so often about 2-3 times a monnth I fall asleep with my little one around 8 and *don't* get back up until 7:30 the next morning.  May seem odd, but I have difficulty getting my mind to shut the heck up.  Also takes the pressure off of &quot;I gotta get to sleep&quot;, which is the worst thing ever.<br>
<br>
/shrug  Dunno if it will help, but I do feel for ya.  I was fortunate?? enough to have this schedule/nonschedule forced into my life for four years....so it wasn't really voluntary.))<br>
